ExternalReferenceType
          Type describing the reference to an corresponding object in an other information system, for example in the german cadastre ALKIS, the german topographic information system or ATKIS, or the OS MasterMap.
GeneralizationRelationType
          Denotes the relation of a _CityObject to its corresponding _CityObject in higher LOD, i.e. to the _CityObjects representing the same real world object in higher LOD.
ImplicitGeometryType
          Type for the implicit representation of a geometry.
ImplicitRepresentationPropertyType
          Denotes the relation of a _CityObject to its implicit geometry representation, which is a representation of a geometry by referencing a prototype and transforming it to its real position in space.
XalAddressPropertyType
          Denotes the relation of an Address feature to the xAL address element.
